Name: despeech
Version: 0.0.2
Summary: Tool for converting direct speech in German into indirect one
Home-page: https://github.com/lnpetrova/despeech
Author: Lidiia Ostyakova
Author-email: lostaaa15@gmail.com
License: UNKNOWN
Description: 
        
        ### Tool for direct speech convertion (for German language)
        
        ## How to install 
        `pip install despeech`
        
        ## How to use
        ```python
        from despeech import DeSpeechConverter
        
        converter = DeSpeechConverter()
        print(converter.convert('Er brummte:"Ich gehe in die Bierstube"'))
        
        ```
